description:
While the table is collapsed, a wood-branded 1 indicates where to expand the first leg uni, while a wood-branded 2 indicates how to expand the second unit.


When the table is expanded, it is the other way around: another wood-branded 1 at a different position indicates which leg unit to move first and second.


The nice thing is that the folding markers for collapsing the table will disappear once the table is collapsed.
